8.000Z","msg":"李怡<br />\n十九<br />\n燒山<br />\n林夕<br />\n<br />\n多次話要泛民應該總辭<br />\n<br />\n大部分人都係咁諗，只係基於對支共邪惡流氓手法了解，普通常識。你班泛民代議士又蠢又廢，尸位素餐，駛撚你代表香港公民咩。"},{"pid":"85323e55096e39785cf64542fd7c8b030886a28f","tid":2281212,"uid":237143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T06:45:33.000Z","msg":"議會抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一日未輸曬都唔可以放棄"},{"pid":"fbfd16dfd547afad38b7c5222b36605c4cbaf16a","tid":2281212,"uid":63782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T06:50:29.000Z","msg":"今日係香港民主最黑暗的一天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}